le to have a good time. If you feel overwhelmed and that you need some help, don\'t hesitate to approach and talk to our marked awareness team or any other staff. We will do the best we can to help you. At the same time, a safer space can only be realized with your help and participation! Therefore we also ask you to respect your own, and other people\'s boundaries. Furthermore, this is not a place for discrimination or hate in the form of racism, sexism, queerphobia, among others. Everyone is welcome at our event, as long as you are respectful to other guests. \nThis is a solidarity event according to the spirit of Provitreff and also our label, which means that we will be donating a part of the possible profit we make to CSD Zürich, as well as the f96 collective. \nWe look forward to seeing you at the rave! \n<3 the Fluidity team\n									\n										 weniger anzeigen','CHF 10.00','Provitreff, Sihlquai 240, Zürich, CH','Party / House & Techno','22:00 Uhr\n									\n																			- \n										06:00 Uhr'),('1699957722-380','https://eventfrog.ch/de/events.html?sc=events&fromDate=2023-12-1&toDate=2023-12-31&page=50&rubrics=914','Tickets\n							\n					\n		\n\n						\n				Dez\n				8\n			\n			\n			\n				Grupo Extra - Mundo Latino Swiss\n									Freitag, 08. Dezember, 22:00\n								CRAZY CLUB, Fribourg (CH)','https://eventfrog.ch/de/p/party/disco/grupo-extra-mundo-latino-swiss-7129937459048080663.html','Grupo Extra - Mundo Latino Swiss',NULL,'Freitag, 08. Dezember, 22:00','Fr., 8. Dezember 2023','¡Saludos amis fribourgeois! \nAprès avoir passé notre première extraordinaire soirée, nous continuons à vous apporter toute l\'énergie, le plaisir et la joie. \nMundo Latino Swiss, nous vous présentons le meilleur groupe de bachata du moment, \nGRUPO EXTRA en concert, avec tous leurs hits, Me Emborrachare, Hoy se Bebe, A Traves del Vaso. \nPour cette merveilleuse deuxième soirée plein de couleurs et de musique, nous avons 2 des meilleurs Dj,s Latinos de Suisse, Mr Boom